{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/truncate-text/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"CSS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bf049282-6b2c-5e06-8fb6-71815eee5a03","excerpt":"If the text is longer than one line, it will be truncated and end with an ellipsis . Explanation  prevents the text from overflowing its dimensions (for a block…","html":"<p>If the text is longer than one line, it will be truncated and end with an ellipsis <code class=\"language-text\">…</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>truncate-text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>If I exceed one line's width, I will be truncated.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.truncate-text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">white-space</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nowrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ellipsis<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>Explanation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">overflow: hidden</code> prevents the text from overflowing its dimensions (for a block, 100% width and auto height).</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">white-space: nowrap</code> prevents the text from exceeding one line in height.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">text-overflow: ellipsis</code> makes it so that if the text exceeds its dimensions, it will end with an ellipsis.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">width: 200px;</code> ensures the element has a dimension, to know when to get ellipsis</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Browser support</h4>\n<p><span class=\"snippet__support-note\">⚠️ Only works for single line elements.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=text-overflow\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=text-overflow</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Truncate text","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/truncate-text/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/zebra-striped-list/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Zebra striped list"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/truncate-text-multiline/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Truncate text multiline"}}}}}